      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DUSTY MCGRAW (6) is a talented type who boasts a strong winning strike-rate at this distance. Jumped well when winning his last couple. Scored latest at Dubbo in a handy 22.94. Ran the fastest time on the program in his latest win. Form reads well for this. SUMMER DREAM (4) was the fastest winner on the program last time out, running away to score by 1.3 lengths (17.96) at Richmond. Solid beginner and with a good start can clear the tricky draw. Looks suited and is one of the contenders. SKEDADDLE MAPLE (2) turned in a moderate run last time when seventh at this track over 365m behind Annie's Rupee (22.53) in a Grade 4/5. Goes very well from this draw with three wins and two minor placings from seven starts. Has ability and can atone. MAYBE NEXT WEEK (1) is a last-start placegetter in a fast-run race - should be thereabouts.",
